---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Warm & Friendly Template | Jobcoach Website" description="Warmes, einladendes Design für Jobcoaches – menschlich, empathisch, nahbar.">
  <div class="demo-page">
    <header class="demo-header">
      <div class="demo-badge">Warm & Friendly Template</div>
      <a href="/order?template=warm" class="btn-use">Dieses Template wählen →</a>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero warm-hero">
      <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
      <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="wave">👋</span>
        <h1>Hallo, ich bin<br/>Maria Schmidt</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Jobcoachin & Therapeutin<br/>Ich glaube daran, dass jeder seinen Weg finden kann – man muss ihn nur sehen lernen.</p>
        
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Empathisch</span>
          <span class="tag">Erfahren</span>
          <span class="tag">Nahbar</span>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="#angebot" class="btn btn-primary">Lerne mich kennen</a>
          <a href="#mehr" class="btn btn-secondary">Mehr erfahren</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="about" id="mehr">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="profile-placeholder">MS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>Über mich</h2>
          <p>Seit über 15 Jahren begleite ich Menschen durch berufliche Krisen und Neuanfänge. Als ausgebildete Therapeutin (TP) und zertifizierte Jobcoach bringe ich sowohl klinische Erfahrung als auch praktische Karriereberatung mit.</p>
          <p>Meine Spezialität: Menschen, die sich verloren fühlen, wieder einen klaren Kompass geben.</p>
          <div class="certs">
            <span>TP (Psychotherapie)</span>
            <span>ICF Associate</span>
            <span>AZWV-Beraterin</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section class="services" id="angebot">
      <h2>Wie ich dir helfen kann</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>Neuanfang-Coaching</h3>
          <p>Für alle, die das Gefühl haben, in ihrer Karriere festzustecken. Gemeinsam finden wir deinen Weg.</p>
          <div class="price">€69<span>/Monat</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">💪</div>
          <h3>Stärken-Coaching</h3>
          <p>Entdecke deine verborgenen Talente und lerne, sie für deine Karriere zu nutzen.</p>
          <div class="price">€89<span>/Monat</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>1:1 Begleitung</h3>
          <p>Intensive Einzelarbeit über 3 Monate. Für tiefgreifende Veränderungen und nachhaltige Ergebnisse.</p>
          <div class="price">€990<span>/Paket</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>Was meine Klienten sagen</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"Maria hat mir geholen, meine Ängste zu überwinden und den Sprung in die Selbstständigkeit zu wagen. Heute bin ich happier als je zuvor."</p>
          <cite>— Jana K., ehem. Projektmanagerin</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"Ich war skeptisch, ob Coaching wirklich hilft. Nach 3 Monaten mit Maria kann ich sagen: Es war die beste Investition in mich selbst."</p>
          <cite>— Peter M., IT-Consultant</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="contact-cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Du bist nicht allein 🌟</h2>
        <p>Berufliche Unsicherheit ist normal. Und es gibt immer einen Weg. Lass uns gemeinsam deinen finden.</p>
        <a href="/order?template=warm" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
          Erstgespräch vereinbaren 💬
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>© 2026 Maria Schmidt Coaching · Change-to-Impact Partner</p>
      <p class="legal-links">
        <a href="/impressum">Impressum</a> · <a href="/datenschutz">Datenschutz</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: #0f172a;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>

<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #d97706;
    --primary-dark: #b45309;
    --accent: #78350f;
    --accent-light: #fbbf24;
    --bg-dark: #0f172a;
    --bg-card: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    --text: #f1f5f9;
    --text-muted: #94a3b8;
  }

  .demo-page { min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

  .demo-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.2);
  }

  .demo-badge {
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
    color: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .btn-use {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-use:hover {
    background: var(--primary-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(100px);
    animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .orb-1 {
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: #d97706;
    top: -100px; left: -100px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .orb-2 {
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    background: #fbbf24;
    bottom: -50px; right: -50px;
    opacity: 0.2;
    animation-delay: -4s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    50% { transform: translate(15px, -15px); }
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 700px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .wave {
    font-size: 4rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    animation: wave 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes wave {
    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    25% { transform: rotate(15deg); }
    75% { transform: rotate(-15deg); }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 550px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
    color: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.4);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fef3c7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(254, 243, 199, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(254, 243, 199, 0.1);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-large { padding: 18px 36px; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .profile-placeholder {
    width: 220px;
    height: 280px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706, #fbbf24);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .certs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .certs span {
    background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.3);
    color: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* Services */
  .services {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .service-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-light);
  }

  .price span { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; }

  /* Testimonials */
  .testimonials {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.05);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1);
  }

  .testimonials h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .stars {
    color: #fbbf24;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonial-card cite {
    color: var(--accent-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .contact-cta {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #fef3c7;
  }

  .contact-cta p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .legal-links { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .legal-links a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-links a:hover { color: var(--accent-light); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .profile-placeholder { margin: 0 auto; }
    .certs { justify-content: center; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>